item.title: About
item.description: Felix Mao is a front-end developer. He graduated from NanChang University in 2014 with a BS in Computer Science. Now He is working at Alibaba Group at Hangzhou, China. Used to worked at NetEase either. You can follow him on Twitter @codediggerfelix, and GitHub, or reach him by email at xunxing1989@gmail.com. If you happen to speak Chinese, you can follow him on 知乎 and 豆瓣.
